### index (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/discounts?page=1&per_page=5
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token

### show
GET http://localhost:8080/api/discounts/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token

### create
POST http://localhost:8080/api/discounts
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tanggal": "2026-08-01",
  "nominal": 150000
}

### create (duplicate date - expect 422 error)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/discounts
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tanggal": "2026-08-01",
  "nominal": 200000
}

### update (only nominal - tanggal is immutable)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/discounts/1
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nominal": 200000
}

### delete
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/discounts/1
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token

### unauthorized (missing token - expect 401)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/discounts
Accept: application/json
